                </section>

                <div class="mf-flow-grid">
                    <section class="mf-flow-canvas-card">
                        <div class="mf-flow-head">
                            <div>
                            <h3>BPMN 2.0 Process Map</h3>
                            <p>Diagnostic QA surface only. Use the builder to change sequence flow, swimlanes, candidate roles, candidate users, timers, gateways, and runtime statuses, then review/approve from the main app board.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mf-flow-chip"><i class="fas fa-circle-play"></i> Start: @_workflowPreview.StartNodeLabel</div>
